{"type": "article", "id": 6057, "title": "Noma 餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-10T07:48:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060600420192xYaGolD8wIsUpd.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t我们 1 月底曾报道过丹麦那个曾经被评选为世界第一餐厅的 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/5699.html\" target=\"_blank\">Noma 打包厨师飞去东京的文华东方酒店开临时店</a>的新闻，现在他们准备把在日本用的餐具拿出来卖了。如果你觉得去吃一顿标价 40200 日元的晚餐太贵的话，那么买买餐具还是可以考虑的。这一次，Noma 不仅为日本单独定制了菜品，还邀请日本当地的陶艺师专门设计定制了餐具，请到了安藤雅信、内田钢一、赤木明登等设计师，定价 40 －320 美元（约合人民币 250－1999 元）不等，<a href=\"http://tokyostore.noma.dk/collections/plateware\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004159sQjyx6GozMC4UmfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004200LvB2WD0V6fHuwAOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004200HoDbwTd1gAFikGB4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004201EBqO8pZbuJC9k4yS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}